  "informal_statement": "For every natural number n, the sum of the first n odd numbers 1 + 3 + ... + (2n-1) equals n^2.",
  "informal_proof_idea": "Induction on n: peel the last term (2k+1) with Finset.sum_range_succ, apply the hypothesis, and k^2 + (2k+1) = (k+1)^2 by ring.",
  "formal_statement_pp": "theorem sum_odds (n : ℕ) : (∑ i ∈ Finset.range n, (2 * i + 1)) = n ^ 2",
